buildECMSArray()

Description
    array buildECMSArray(mixed $array)
	If the parameter is an array, returns a string containing a string representation of all the array elements in the same order, with the string 
	stored in $engineVars['delim'] between each element.
	
Parameters
    array
		A variable of any type may be passed to the function.  The function handles array and non-array types accordingly.
		
Return Values
    Returns a string if the parameter passed to the function is an array.  Returns the original parameter otherwise.